🔥 MusicLang Space is now live on Hugging Face 🤗 (link below ⬇️)

Experience the power of MusicLang, a controllable model designed for music generation:

🦙 > Discover the LLAMA2 architecture, meticulously trained from scratch for symbolic music generation, ensuring exceptional quality;
👨‍🎨 > Unleash your creativity by extending an existing music, or create new ones from scratch;
💻 > Seamlessly integrate MusicLang into your applications, with an inference optimized for CPUs written in C, other integrations and optimizations coming soon.

In the space, you’ll find everything you need to:

1️⃣ Install the package from our GitHub;
2️⃣ Explore the model through our demo;
3️⃣ Generate your own sounds;
4️⃣ Dive deeper into the technical details under the hood.

Help us share the future of music composition! Spread the word, show your support by adding a star or contribute to our project. ⭐️

